<hr data-start="142" data-end="145">
<h2 data-section-id="1p1teoy" data-start="147" data-end="193">✅ 1. If you are using Git (recommended way)</h2>
<p data-start="195" data-end="271">👉 You must run the code in <strong data-start="223" data-end="271">Terminal / Command Prompt / VS Code terminal</strong></p>
<h3 data-section-id="1aw5ay5" data-start="273" data-end="286">📍 Steps:</h3>
<ol data-start="287" data-end="429">
<li data-section-id="1dymo58" data-start="287" data-end="314">
<p data-start="290" data-end="314">Open your project folder</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="ohtmeb" data-start="315" data-end="410">
<p data-start="318" data-end="410">Open terminal in that folder<br data-start="346" data-end="349">
(Right click → <em data-start="367" data-end="385">Open in Terminal</em> OR use VS Code terminal)</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="rnyyhf" data-start="412" data-end="429">
<p data-start="415" data-end="429">Paste and run:</p>
</li>
</ol>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="431" data-end="583"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-iapvo518.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Bash</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-iapvo518.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼd">git</span><span> init</span><br><span class="ͼd">git</span><span> add .</span><br><span class="ͼd">git</span><span> commit </span><span class="ͼf">-m</span><span> </span><span class="ͼc">"first commit"</span><br><span class="ͼd">git</span><span> remote add origin https://github.com/your-username/repo-name.git</span><br><span class="ͼd">git</span><span> push </span><span class="ͼf">-u</span><span> origin main</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="585" data-end="653">👉 If using <strong data-start="597" data-end="608">Git LFS</strong>, run those commands <strong data-start="629" data-end="653">in the same terminal</strong></p>
<hr data-start="655" data-end="658">
<h2 data-section-id="61wym2" data-start="660" data-end="713">✅ 2. If you are using GitHub website (no terminal)</h2>
<p data-start="715" data-end="753">👉 Then you <strong data-start="727" data-end="745">DON’T add code</strong> — just:</p>
<ul data-start="754" data-end="798">
<li data-section-id="w2uvo0" data-start="754" data-end="778">
<p data-start="756" data-end="778">Click <strong data-start="762" data-end="778">Upload files</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="wdwiqq" data-start="779" data-end="798">
<p data-start="781" data-end="798">Drag &amp; drop files</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="800" data-end="847">⚠️ But this only works for files <strong data-start="833" data-end="847">under 25MB</strong></p>
<hr data-start="849" data-end="852">
<h2 data-section-id="1oi3qpx" data-start="854" data-end="896">✅ 3. If using Git LFS (for large files)</h2>
<p data-start="898" data-end="954">👉 Again, run in <strong data-start="915" data-end="954">terminal inside your project folder</strong></p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="956" data-end="1089"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-iapvo518.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>Bash</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-iapvo518.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼd">git</span><span> lfs install</span><br><span class="ͼd">git</span><span> lfs track </span><span class="ͼc">"*.zip"</span><br><span class="ͼd">git</span><span> add .gitattributes</span><br><span class="ͼd">git</span><span> add yourfile.zip</span><br><span class="ͼd">git</span><span> commit </span><span class="ͼf">-m</span><span> </span><span class="ͼc">"Add large file"</span><br><span class="ͼd">git</span><span> push</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="1091" data-end="1094">
<h2 data-section-id="1iia3sh" data-start="1096" data-end="1138">🧠 Simple understanding (remember this)</h2>
<ul data-start="1140" data-end="1294">
<li data-section-id="1mkmxdy" data-start="1140" data-end="1189">
<p data-start="1142" data-end="1189">💻 <strong data-start="1145" data-end="1189">Terminal = for commands (git, lfs, etc.)</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="11xihwn" data-start="1190" data-end="1238">
<p data-start="1192" data-end="1238">🌐 <strong data-start="1195" data-end="1238">GitHub website = only for small uploads</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="z8jmpi" data-start="1239" data-end="1294">
<p data-start="1241" data-end="1294">📁 <strong data-start="1244" data-end="1294">Project folder = where your files + code exist</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1296" data-end="1299">
<h2 data-section-id="o18nyt" data-start="1301" data-end="1325">⚡ Quick Tip (for you)</h2>
<p data-start="1326" data-end="1357">Since you’re learning frontend:</p>
<ul data-start="1358" data-end="1475">
<li data-section-id="9znt9v" data-start="1358" data-end="1429">
<p data-start="1360" data-end="1429">Always open your project in <strong data-start="1388" data-end="1429"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Visual Studio Code</span></span></strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="vpw63w" data-start="1430" data-end="1475">
<p data-start="1432" data-end="1475">Use its <strong data-start="1440" data-end="1461">built-in terminal</strong> → easiest way</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="1477" data-end="1480">
<p data-start="1482" data-end="1626" data-is-last-node="" data-is-only-node="">If you want, I can guide you step-by-step for your exact project 👍<br data-start="1549" data-end="1552">
Just tell me:<br>
👉 what file you are trying to upload (zip? video? project?)</p></div></div></div></div><div class="z-0 flex min-h-[46px] justify-start"><div aria-label="Response actions" class="touch:-me-2 touch:-ms-3.5 -ms-2.5 -me-1 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-y-4 p-1 select-none touch:w-[calc(100%+--spacing(3.5))] -mt-1 w-[calc(100%+--spacing(2.5))] duration-[1.5s] focus-within:transition-none hover:transition-none touch:pointer-events-auto pointer-events-none [mask-image:linear-gradient(to_right,black_33%,transparent_66%)] [mask-size:300%_100%] [mask-position:100%_0%] motion-safe:transition-[mask-position] group-hover/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-hover/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] group-focus-within/turn-messages:pointer-events-auto group-focus-within/turn-messages:[mask-position:0_0] has-data-[state=open]:pointer-events-auto has-data-[state=open]:[mask-position:0_0]" role="group" tabindex="-1" style="mask-position: 0% 0%;"><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Copy response" data-testid="copy-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-iapvo518.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Good response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="good-response-turn-action-button" data-state="closed"><span class="flex items-center justify-center touch:w-10 h-8 w-8"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-iapvo518.svg#51753c" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></button><button class="text-token-text-secondary hover:bg-token-bg-secondary rounded-lg" aria-label="Bad response" aria-pressed="false" data-testid="bad-response-turn-ac