<hr data-start="122" data-end="125">
<h2 data-section-id="c75q2z" data-start="127" data-end="150">✅ What you should do</h2>
<h3 data-section-id="1f2pmb3" data-start="152" data-end="185">🔹 Option 1 (Best for GitHub)</h3>
<p data-start="186" data-end="234">👉 <strong data-start="189" data-end="234">Extract both ZIP files and upload folders</strong></p>
<p data-start="236" data-end="266">So your repo should look like:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="268" data-end="416"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-iapvo518.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>project/</span><br><span> ├── blood_test/</span><br><span> │    ├── index.html</span><br><span> │    ├── style.css</span><br><span> │    └── script.js</span><br><span> ├── blood_group_data/</span><br><span> │    └── (your dataset files)</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="418" data-end="492">✔ This looks <strong data-start="431" data-end="447">professional</strong><br>
✔ Easy for others to understand your project</p>
<hr data-start="494" data-end="497">
<h3 data-section-id="o46gou" data-start="499" data-end="539">🔹 Option 2 (If you really want ZIP)</h3>
<p data-start="540" data-end="602">You can upload both ZIP files directly — they are under limit.</p>
<p data-start="604" data-end="640">But ❗ not recommended for portfolio.</p>
<hr data-start="642" data-end="645">
<h2 data-section-id="hy50a2" data-start="647" data-end="695">🔥 Best approach for YOU (frontend developer)</h2>
<p data-start="697" data-end="731">Since you're building a portfolio:</p>
<ul data-start="732" data-end="827">
<li data-section-id="qur3ep" data-start="732" data-end="775">
<p data-start="734" data-end="775">Keep <strong data-start="739" data-end="764">UI code (HTML/CSS/JS)</strong> separate</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ixunfb" data-start="776" data-end="827">
<p data-start="778" data-end="827">Keep <strong data-start="783" data-end="802">data (CSV/JSON)</strong> in a folder like <code data-start="820" data-end="827">/data</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="829" data-end="837">Example:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="838" data-end="930"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-iapvo518.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>blood-project/</span><br><span> ├── index.html</span><br><span> ├── css/</span><br><span> ├── js/</span><br><span> └── data/</span><br><span>     └── blood_data.csv</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="932" data-end="935">
