<p data-start="953" data-end="959">I can:</p>
<ul data-start="960" data-end="1105">
<li data-section-id="ey7pdt" data-start="960" data-end="982">
<p data-start="962" data-end="982">Extract both files</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1o4kgsz" data-start="983" data-end="1026">
<p data-start="985" data-end="1026">Organize into a clean project structure</p>
