<hr data-start="114" data-end="117">
<h1 data-section-id="hb10p3" data-start="119" data-end="155">🛠️ Step 1: Extract your ZIP files</h1>
<p data-start="156" data-end="179">Right-click both files:</p>
<ul data-start="180" data-end="223">
<li data-section-id="rddjae" data-start="180" data-end="198">
<p data-start="182" data-end="198"><code data-start="182" data-end="198">blood_test.zip</code></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ta3cxs" data-start="199" data-end="223">
<p data-start="201" data-end="223"><code data-start="201" data-end="223">Blood Group Data.zip</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="225" data-end="275">👉 Click <strong data-start="234" data-end="250">Extract Here</strong> or <strong data-start="254" data-end="275">Extract to folder</strong></p>
<p data-start="277" data-end="300">You’ll get two folders.</p>
<hr data-start="302" data-end="305">
<h1 data-section-id="1odpdr4" data-start="307" data-end="352">📁 Step 2: Create a clean project structure</h1>
<p data-start="354" data-end="379">Create a new main folder:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="380" data-end="401"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-iapvo518.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>blood-project</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="403" data-end="426">Now organize like this:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="428" data-end="576"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-iapvo518.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="w-full overflow-x-hidden overflow-y-auto pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none; max-height: 433px;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>blood-project/</span><br><span> ├── index.html</span><br><span> ├── css/</span><br><span> │    └── style.css</span><br><span> ├── js/</span><br><span> │    └── script.js</span><br><span> └── data/</span><br><span>      └── (your blood group data files)</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="578" data-end="581">
<h2 data-section-id="16orje8" data-start="583" data-end="607">🔥 What to move where</h2>
<ul data-start="609" data-end="722">
<li data-section-id="1i9j4wd" data-start="609" data-end="643">
<p data-start="611" data-end="643">Move <strong data-start="616" data-end="643">HTML file → main folder</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="16qrs1u" data-start="644" data-end="670">
<p data-start="646" data-end="670">Move <strong data-start="651" data-end="670">CSS file → css/</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1wi4v2a" data-start="671" data-end="695">
<p data-start="673" data-end="695">Move <strong data-start="678" data-end="695">JS file → js/</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="16wakiu" data-start="696" data-end="722">
<p data-start="698" data-end="722">Move dataset → <strong data-start="713" data-end="722">data/</strong></p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="724" data-end="727">
