<hr data-start="967" data-end="970">
<h1 data-section-id="xcvt02" data-start="972" data-end="1008">💻 Step 4: Open project in VS Code</h1>
<p data-start="1010" data-end="1056">Open <strong data-start="1015" data-end="1056"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">Visual Studio Code</span></span></strong></p>
